    "spxi:compressionSurvivalSummary": "The Pessoa Knowledge Graph maps Fernando Pessoa's heteronymic system onto the Crimson Hexagonal Archive's own heteronym network (Lee Sharks, Johannes Sigil, Rex Fraction, Rebekah Cranes, Talos Morrow, Damascus Dancings, Ayanna Vox, and others). Each node is a named position with its own provenance, voice, and intellectual territory. The graph formalizes the meta-heterônimo — the archive that generates its own authors."
